{"tid":2021192,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"央視製作反修例事件影片 批評革命分子將香港拖向深淵","createTime":"2020-05-17T14:40:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T08:39:43.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"4cacf73bc8286f4b587c8522dd68cedf6687db95","tid":2021192,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T14:40:00.000Z","msg":"央視反修例事件<del>紀錄片</del>批亂港分子將港拖向危險深淵<br />\n17.05.2020 22:20<br />\n<br />\n央視播出有關香港反修例事件的紀綠片《另一個香港》，分為「香港之亂」及「風從何來」兩集，講述陳同佳殺人案引發港府修訂逃犯修例，之後觸發連串示威及破壞，指亂港分子將香港拖向危險的深淵。紀錄片又訪問多名中外學者、市民，以及曾被搶槍的葵涌警署警長劉澤基，批評示威者的破壞行為。紀綠片形容這場示威令香港遭遇一場浩劫，而背後有美國等西方反華勢力支持，包括點名批評李柱銘、黎智英、陳方安生及黃之鋒等人。紀錄片又批評教協煽動學生到維園示威，副會長葉建源美化主張港獨的青年有主見。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1288090&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1288090%26csid%3D261_341&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCSukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=68b5b660\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1288090&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"6632f401f91d64a7b4f6d306489f66327516b759","tid":2021192,"uid":100581,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:40:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢單野好似當年新彊開頭咁，<br />\n又係出所謂「專題片」黎先挑起國內情緒<br />\n</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"4d4d8842dc9b54a2e5579abb8fa73105f4396cd8","tid":2021192,"uid":21545,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"6632f401f91d64a7b4f6d306489f66327516b759","tid":2021192,"uid":100581,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:40:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢單野好似當年新彊開頭咁，<br />\n又係出所謂「專題片」黎先挑起國內情緒<br />\n</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:41:52.000Z","msg":"夏寶龍以前管新疆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"